(Don't mind me, Hotmail is screwing up. I think Dark Mouse is out of the 
base, right?)

Quickstrike:





Quickstrike kept going forward. He sensed the nerve gas that Black Arachnia 
said she saw going to release. She did keep her word. If she was going to 
hit you, by Primus she was going to hit you. He backed up, and shifted his 
long body until he could turn around. He passed the main computer room and 
came to a different vent face. He punched it out with a very large claw. He 
crawled down the wall of the room.

He transformed to robot mode and looked around. From the looks of it, he was 
in the engine room. He knew now that he wasn't going to get a chance to do 
what Megatron told him to do.

He had a crazy, suicial idea. Surrender.
